Their actions during the marriage says a lot about them if what they allege is true.
*My point is, either way they look bad*
How can Amber's friends and sister live in a place paid by the person that is hurting your sister/friend?
Like I'll try my best to tell my sister/friend to leave that relationship. And move out of that place.
Why were they living there in the first place? And see how Amber wanted to keep that house?
Like, I wouldn't want to live in a place I associate with being beaten.

I understand for poor/middle class people, they keep the house because they got no other option, but people with more money usually leave/sell the house.
Ofcourse, it depends how traumatizing the situation was.
